Say whhaattt!!! No more bad hair days?! No more humidity messing up what I just did?! 😩🙌🏽 Now I can do my hair in the park, in the car, at the gym, or do some touch ups before an event or date!! Aaayyyy!!!! @Ghd_NorthAmerica created a cordless styler yall! Style/touch up your hair with 20 minutes of use anywhere you are using the new unplugged styler! 🔥

#unplugged #nostringsattatched #ghdpartner

node.text: Imagine walking out like this with only 20% of your makeup done? 🧐  #AD Do y’all know that still in 2021 80% of search results for beautiful women DO NOT show women of color? That means only 20% of us show up!!!🤦🏽‍♀️ I’m so happy @Olay is helping to #DecodeTheBias and change that!🙌🏽 They are helping the future generation of women in STEM by sending over 1,000 girls of color to code camp (up to 1,200 total)! Let’s goooo!!!!! 🔥
